rows.label: qst701802_msg0001
rows.name:
That's everything we need.
Shall we get started right away?

rows.label: qst701802_msg0004
rows.name:
I feel like I'm just stabbing myself in
the fingers over and over again! Doing
this stupid emblem was a big mistake!

rows.label: qst701802_msg0005
rows.name: This is bad. This is incredibly bad.

rows.label: qst701802_msg0006
rows.name:
So you're a little hamfisted.
Why not try something easier?

rows.label: qst701802_msg0007
rows.name:
You don't understand!
That would be pointless!

rows.label: qst701802_msg0008
rows.name:
It doesn't matter how difficult it is.
I have to do this. It's this or bust.

rows.label: qst701802_msg0011
rows.name:
You're like "oh, he'll get there someday"
but who knows how long that'll take?
I have to be good at this RIGHT NOW.

rows.label: qst701802_msg0012
rows.name: I don't have time to waste.

rows.label: qst701802_msg0014
rows.name:
Listen. Why don't I make you
an example to follow first?

rows.label: qst701802_msg0015
rows.name:
I'll sew the Iira emblem onto one of
my usual talismans, so you've got
something to work off of. All right?
